OL,5,Chatred
OL,7,FThree men have been remanded in
OL,8,Fcustody after appearing in court
OL,9,Fcharged with distributing or
OL,10,Fpublishing material intended to stir
OL,11,Fup racial hatred.
OL,13,FAll three appeared before Cardiff
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on Monday, 12
OL,15,FAugust.
OL,17,FGeraint Boyce, 43, of Penrhiw-Fer,
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to publishing written
OL,19,Fmaterial intended t stir up racial
OL,20,Fhatred following the deaths of three
OL,21,Fgirls in Southport last month.
