OL,3,CThree charged over Facebook posts
OL,4,Callegedly intended to stir up racial
OL,5,Chatred
OL,7,FThe court heard that he had reposted
OL,8,Fan image of a mosque on Facebook with
OL,9,Fthe caption "no more mosques - share
OL,10,Fif you agree".
OL,12,FIn a separate post, he had posted the
OL,13,Fcomment "burn them (the mosques) all
OL,14,Fdown".JBoyce was remanded in custody
OL,15,Fand will appear at Merthyr Crown Court
OL,16,Fon Friday, 16 August, for sentencing.
OL,18,FDaffron Thomas Williams also appeared
OL,19,Fin court, and pleaded guilty to
OL,20,Fdistributing written material with
OL,21,Fintent to stir up racial hatred.
