OL,3,CThree charged over Facebook posts
OL,4,Callegedly intended to stir up racial
OL,5,Chatred
OL,7,FThe court heard the charge related to
OL,8,Fa number of posts he had made on
OL,9,FFacebook, with one suggesting that the
OL,10,Findividual charged with murdering
OL,11,Fthree young girls in Southport was a
OL,12,FMuslim and an immigrant. The 17-year-
OL,13,Fold boy who has been charged was born
OL,14,Fin Cardiff, police have said.
OL,16,FIn another post, Williams wrote that
OL,17,F"civil war is the next step" and that
OL,18,F"they want us to (become) Islamic".
