OL,8,FBless Tommy Robinson", a reference to
OL,9,Fthe founder of the now defunct far-
OL,10,Fright organisation the English Defence
OL,11,FLeague.
OL,13,FWilliams' solicitor said her client
OL,14,Fhad been "extremely troubled" by the
OL,15,Frecent social disorder and had taken
OL,16,Fresponsibility for his actions.
OL,18,FShe also said the defendant suffered
OL,19,Fwith post-traumatic stress disorder
OL,20,Fafter serving in the army.
